description: [``botocore``] This release introduces support for Voice Connector media metrics in the Amazon Chime SDK Voice namespace

[``botocore``] CloudFront now supports block lists in origin request policies so that you can forward all headers, cookies, or query string from viewer requests to the origin *except* for those specified in the block list.
[``botocore``] AWS DataSync has relaxed the minimum length constraint of AccessKey for Object Storage locations to 1.

[``botocore``] This release lets customers configure Off-peak window and software update related properties for a new/existing domain. It enhances the capabilities of StartServiceSoftwareUpdate API; adds 2 new APIs - ListScheduledActions & UpdateScheduledAction; and allows Auto-tune to make use of Off-peak window.
[``botocore``] CloudWatch RUM now supports CloudWatch Custom Metrics
